IR:

* Iron Raptor strays from prowl a bit, her snout on the ground and 
constantly looking for the signature of Iris.
She just finds the location where Iris was and was just about to thrust in a 
claw to dig her out when Prowl gives a shout.
Lifting her head and looking towards him.

Iron Raptor hops into action and trots over to him, looking down to where he 
was pointing. She lowers her snoud and finds herself smelling the scent of a 
bot, then lifting her snout back up with a sigh.*

" There's a bot there but I can't sense a spark signature..."

* Perhaps, another Maximal dead. Just what they needed.*
